== Umusozi wa Rebero ==
Umusozi wa Rebero ni umusozi umwe mu misozi iri mumujyi wa [[Kigali]] kandi ubitse byinshi mumateka yu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]]

ni umusozi uherereye mu Karere ka kicukiro kandi ukikijwe nimirenge itandukanye nka [[Umurenge wa Kigali|Gikondo]], Nyamirambo

[[Umurenge wa Mageragere|Mageragere]] niyindi. uyumusozi ufite ubwiza nyaburanga butandukanye harimo amashyamba ubusitani nibindi

byiza byinshyi bibereye ijisho <ref>http://www.igicumbi.com/index.php/ubukerarugendo-mu-rwanda/ibyiza-nyaburanga/item/430-ibintu-byo-gusura-ku-musozi-wa-rebero</ref> 

== Ubukungu ==
[[Umurenge wa Rwezamenyo|Umusozi wa Rebero]] ni Umusozi ukurura ba mukerarugendo kubera ibyiza ndanga murage biwugize

cyane ko ariwo musozi uriho iminara myinshi yifashishwa mwisakaza majwi ndetse namashusho<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4m4yBwH--JM</ref>

== Amateka ==
umusozi wa Rebero kandi niho Inkotanyi zanyuze mugufata umujyi wa [[Kigali]] murugamba 

rwo guhagarika [[Genocide mu Rwanda|Genocide]] yakorewe abatutsi muwi 1994<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/amateka-yihariye-y-uburyo-inkotanyi-zafashe-rebero-mu-1994-bigasaza-u-bufaransa</ref> ku itariki 11 mata

== Ubuzima ==
umusozi wa Rebero ni umusozi mwiza ugizwe nishyamba nubusitani bwiza 

cyane ko ari numusozi ukorerwaho imyitozo ngorora mubiri<ref>https://web.facebook.com/permalink.php?id=604005269751818&story_fbid=1011085559043785&_rdc=1&_rdr</ref> nabatari bake

== Ibigize umusozi wa Rebero ==
Umusozi wa Rebero ugizwe nibyiza nyaburanga byinshi harimo ninzu ndangamurage

iminara, ubusitani, amashuri, ndetse nurwibutso rwa Genocide yakorewe abatutsi<ref>https://www.kicukiro.gov.rw/akarere/menya-akarere</ref>

